1
00:01:49,060 --> 00:01:54,580
=Eight Hundred=

2
00:01:57,740 --> 00:02:01,580
=Episode 20=
(Chinese New Year's Eve)

3
00:02:19,980 --> 00:02:20,820
Mr. Chen,

4
00:02:21,260 --> 00:02:22,540
it's getting late.

5
00:02:22,540 --> 00:02:23,780
Why don't we eat first?

6
00:02:28,180 --> 00:02:29,020
Dad.

7
00:02:30,500 --> 00:02:31,340
What's on your mind?

8
00:03:23,460 --> 00:03:24,300
Hui.

9
00:03:24,500 --> 00:03:25,340
Lately,

10
00:03:25,340 --> 00:03:26,980
I keep thinking about

11
00:03:27,300 --> 00:03:28,660
when you were little.

12
00:03:29,980 --> 00:03:30,860
What about that?

13
00:03:31,740 --> 00:03:32,620
Back then...

14
00:03:35,710 --> 00:03:36,860
You were only three or four.

15
00:03:40,460 --> 00:03:41,500
I used to always ask you,

16
00:03:43,060 --> 00:03:44,180
what do you want to be

17
00:03:44,940 --> 00:03:45,860
when you grow up?

18
00:03:48,020 --> 00:03:48,860
What did I say?

19
00:03:49,540 --> 00:03:51,420
Every single time,

20
00:03:51,420 --> 00:03:52,900
your answer was different.

21
00:03:52,900 --> 00:03:53,740
Because of that,

22
00:03:56,180 --> 00:03:57,820
I never really knew

23
00:03:59,100 --> 00:04:00,040
what you'd end up doing

24
00:04:01,540 --> 00:04:02,700
once you grew up.

25
00:04:07,060 --> 00:04:08,540
Aren't things great right now?

26
00:04:09,260 --> 00:04:10,420
Our family

27
00:04:10,420 --> 00:04:11,620
is doing better and better.

28
00:04:12,900 --> 00:04:13,740
Yeah.

29
00:04:17,060 --> 00:04:18,140
Better and better.

30
00:04:20,500 --> 00:04:21,340
Songge.

31
00:04:24,860 --> 00:04:26,580
Do you know how to drive?

32
00:04:30,140 --> 00:04:30,980
Mr. Chen,

33
00:04:31,700 --> 00:04:32,980
how could I know how to drive?

34
00:04:33,460 --> 00:04:34,300
You forgot.

35
00:04:34,380 --> 00:04:35,580
I was so sick back then,

36
00:04:35,700 --> 00:04:36,980
no driving school would take me.

37
00:04:44,780 --> 00:04:47,350
The night Yang Baichun
had his incident,

38
00:04:47,780 --> 00:04:48,780
both of you

39
00:04:50,300 --> 00:04:51,540
were at the coking plant.

40
00:04:53,620 --> 00:04:54,460
Yes.

41
00:04:56,180 --> 00:04:57,340
Huo Kaiming was there too.

42
00:05:50,300 --> 00:05:51,260
What about Yang Baichun?

43
00:05:54,940 --> 00:05:58,100
Fire!

44
00:05:58,100 --> 00:05:59,020
There's a fire!

45
00:05:59,260 --> 00:06:00,100
Fire!

46
00:06:00,100 --> 00:06:01,270
Where's the fire?

47
00:06:01,690 --> 00:06:02,850
Fengyang Coal Mine!

48
00:06:02,920 --> 00:06:04,410
- Fengyang Coal Mine?
- It's on fire!

49
00:06:04,420 --> 00:06:05,460
That closed down ages ago.

50
00:06:05,460 --> 00:06:06,610
- What is this nonsense?
- It's on fire!

51
00:06:06,610 --> 00:06:07,490
Fire!

52
00:06:08,220 --> 00:06:09,300
You two, go put it out!

53
00:06:09,300 --> 00:06:10,420
- No...
- Put out the fire!

54
00:06:10,420 --> 00:06:11,260
I'm a police officer!

55
00:06:11,260 --> 00:06:12,820
Where do you live? What's your name?

56
00:06:12,820 --> 00:06:13,660
My name is...

57
00:06:13,660 --> 00:06:14,780
My name is Chen Hongbing.

58
00:06:14,780 --> 00:06:15,820
I'm a cop!

59
00:06:15,820 --> 00:06:16,900
Hurry and put out the fire!

60
00:06:16,900 --> 00:06:18,100
Where did this lunatic come from?

61
00:06:18,100 --> 00:06:18,980
Just ignore him.

62
00:06:18,980 --> 00:06:19,830
Go away!

63
00:06:20,420 --> 00:06:22,380
Hurry and put it out!

64
00:06:22,380 --> 00:06:23,700
Put out the fire!

65
00:06:24,110 --> 00:06:24,970
Wait, Dad.

66
00:06:25,900 --> 00:06:27,140
It's the Chinese New Year.

67
00:06:27,140 --> 00:06:28,140
What's wrong?

68
00:06:28,140 --> 00:06:28,980
Have you forgotten?

69
00:06:29,060 --> 00:06:30,220
The police already checked.

70
00:06:30,320 --> 00:06:32,060
I was at home having dinner that day.

71
00:06:33,620 --> 00:06:36,060
When I arrived
at the crime scene that day,

72
00:06:38,020 --> 00:06:38,860
I noticed that

73
00:06:39,500 --> 00:06:40,780
the driver's seat

74
00:06:41,140 --> 00:06:42,420
in Yang Baichun's car

75
00:06:42,420 --> 00:06:43,740
was pushed incredibly far forward.

76
00:06:44,020 --> 00:06:45,460
It would only fit

77
00:06:46,540 --> 00:06:47,620
a woman.

78
00:06:49,740 --> 00:06:51,220
And that Mercedes you were driving

79
00:06:51,220 --> 00:06:52,060
has the seats

80
00:06:52,060 --> 00:06:53,140
with a memory function.

81
00:06:54,060 --> 00:06:55,460
That button must've been

82
00:06:55,460 --> 00:06:56,860
programmed to remember

83
00:06:57,980 --> 00:07:00,100
Songge's driving position, right?

84
00:07:02,940 --> 00:07:03,780
Mr. Chen.

85
00:07:04,100 --> 00:07:05,500
I don't know how to drive.

86
00:07:05,500 --> 00:07:06,700
I don't have a license either.

87
00:07:09,700 --> 00:07:10,540
Hui.

88
00:07:10,540 --> 00:07:12,180
It must have been you

89
00:07:13,220 --> 00:07:14,260
who had Songge

90
00:07:15,300 --> 00:07:17,260
put on Yang Baichun's clothes,

91
00:07:18,500 --> 00:07:19,740
drive his car

92
00:07:19,740 --> 00:07:21,060
to Zhangtou Village,

93
00:07:21,060 --> 00:07:22,100
and take a spin around.

94
00:07:22,820 --> 00:07:24,740
You created the illusion

95
00:07:26,060 --> 00:07:28,900
that at 9:00 PM,
nothing had happened to Yang Baichun.

96
00:07:29,920 --> 00:07:31,020
Yang Baichun lost his mind.

97
00:07:31,900 --> 00:07:33,420
No one will believe a word he says.

98
00:07:33,420 --> 00:07:34,980
Now, do exactly as I tell you.

99
00:07:39,820 --> 00:07:42,060
(You put Huo Kaiming's body
into the car.)

100
00:07:42,060 --> 00:07:43,460
(There was a bag inside.)

101
00:07:43,460 --> 00:07:44,320
(I prepared)

102
00:07:44,320 --> 00:07:45,300
(clean clothes for you)

103
00:07:45,300 --> 00:07:46,790
(and Yang Baichun's jacket too.)

104
00:07:48,380 --> 00:07:49,580
(I'll tell you what to do)

105
00:07:49,580 --> 00:07:50,780
(once we're on the road.)

106
00:07:55,300 --> 00:07:56,620
And you,

107
00:07:56,620 --> 00:07:57,460
Hui...

108
00:07:57,860 --> 00:07:59,180
You drove off,

109
00:07:59,180 --> 00:08:01,140
got rid of the murder weapon,

110
00:08:01,140 --> 00:08:02,340
and drove back to Fengyang.

111
00:08:18,020 --> 00:08:18,860
Director Chen.

112
00:08:20,220 --> 00:08:21,060
Look.

113
00:08:26,500 --> 00:08:27,500
But back then,

114
00:08:28,660 --> 00:08:29,860
there was one thing

115
00:08:32,020 --> 00:08:33,140
I couldn't figure out.

116
00:08:33,660 --> 00:08:34,860
Neither of you

117
00:08:34,860 --> 00:08:36,300
had the time

118
00:08:36,300 --> 00:08:38,660
to dispose of Huo Kaiming's body

119
00:08:38,660 --> 00:08:41,620
and burn Yang Baichun's car.

120
00:08:41,620 --> 00:08:43,180
Then, it suddenly hit me.

121
00:08:45,500 --> 00:08:46,900
Those guys selling cough syrup

122
00:08:46,900 --> 00:08:48,180
told me

123
00:08:48,180 --> 00:08:49,220
that their contact,

124
00:08:49,220 --> 00:08:50,740
the woman with the scar,

125
00:08:52,940 --> 00:08:54,140
rode a motorcycle.

126
00:08:55,580 --> 00:08:56,740
If I'm not mistaken,

127
00:08:57,940 --> 00:08:58,780
Songge,

128
00:09:00,420 --> 00:09:01,940
that night,

129
00:09:01,940 --> 00:09:03,580
you rode your motorcycle

130
00:09:04,620 --> 00:09:05,860
back to the hotel.

131
00:09:06,940 --> 00:09:08,060
It's thirty minutes faster

132
00:09:08,540 --> 00:09:09,740
than driving.

133
00:09:10,980 --> 00:09:11,820
So,

134
00:09:13,220 --> 00:09:14,740
you were the only one, Songge,

135
00:09:15,860 --> 00:09:17,580
who could have pulled it off.

136
00:09:54,780 --> 00:09:55,980
(And you were able to)

137
00:09:55,980 --> 00:09:58,420
(make it back to the hotel)

138
00:09:58,420 --> 00:09:59,820
before midnight,

139
00:10:02,780 --> 00:10:04,140
where you ran into Kang Limin.

140
00:10:13,100 --> 00:10:13,940
Limin.

141
00:10:25,500 --> 00:10:26,340
Dad.

142
00:10:26,340 --> 00:10:27,180
That's

143
00:10:27,420 --> 00:10:28,790
all just speculation.

144
00:10:29,580 --> 00:10:30,580
It's not evidence.

145
00:10:40,300 --> 00:10:41,140
Hui.

146
00:10:41,780 --> 00:10:43,500
You don't know me at all.

147
00:10:54,140 --> 00:10:56,260
The police have already found

148
00:10:56,260 --> 00:10:58,700
Huo Kaiming's body
and the stun baton at the coal plant.

149
00:11:04,780 --> 00:11:06,460
(The pawnshop owner identified you.)

150
00:11:06,460 --> 00:11:07,620
(He said you bought)

151
00:11:07,620 --> 00:11:08,820
(that stun baton)

152
00:11:08,820 --> 00:11:11,260
(from him on the day of the murder.)

153
00:11:11,260 --> 00:11:13,260
(And we found)

154
00:11:13,260 --> 00:11:14,820
(both Yang Baichun's)

155
00:11:14,820 --> 00:11:16,860
(and Huo Kaiming's skin tissue on it.)

156
00:11:18,860 --> 00:11:19,700
It's my fault.

157
00:11:23,540 --> 00:11:24,660
I should have

158
00:11:24,660 --> 00:11:26,060
stopped you sooner.

159
00:11:27,300 --> 00:11:29,140
I let things go this far.

160
00:11:31,340 --> 00:11:32,180
It's my fault.

161
00:11:40,100 --> 00:11:42,020
Dad, Mom isn't even back yet.

162
00:11:43,120 --> 00:11:44,920
We haven't had
our Chinese New Year's dinner.

163
00:11:45,500 --> 00:11:46,990
Let's just have a nice dinner, okay?

164
00:11:47,420 --> 00:11:48,260
Dad?

165
00:11:55,300 --> 00:11:56,340
Forgive me.

166
00:12:18,220 --> 00:12:19,060
I thought...

167
00:12:21,980 --> 00:12:23,900
I thought we could start all over again.

168
00:12:25,100 --> 00:12:26,090
I thought our family

169
00:12:26,090 --> 00:12:27,500
had finally patched things up.

170
00:12:30,020 --> 00:12:30,860
Mr. Chen.

171
00:12:32,500 --> 00:12:33,620
Please, let Hui go.

172
00:12:33,620 --> 00:12:34,460
Please!

173
00:12:35,100 --> 00:12:36,540
It's all my fault.

174
00:12:36,540 --> 00:12:37,740
Arrest me.

175
00:12:37,740 --> 00:12:38,600
Don't arrest Hui.

176
00:12:38,600 --> 00:12:39,980
He didn't know anything.

177
00:12:39,980 --> 00:12:41,220
It's all my fault!

178
00:12:42,180 --> 00:12:43,020
Songge.

179
00:12:43,620 --> 00:12:45,140
It's all my fault!

180
00:12:47,260 --> 00:12:48,140
It's too late.

181
00:12:50,740 --> 00:12:52,380
It's too late,

182
00:12:52,380 --> 00:12:53,220
my girl.

183
00:12:58,780 --> 00:13:00,380
It's too late.

184
00:13:02,100 --> 00:13:02,940
Dad...

185
00:13:08,940 --> 00:13:10,420
We let you down.

186
00:13:16,380 --> 00:13:17,780
I was too naive.

187
00:13:22,940 --> 00:13:23,820
I never thought...

188
00:13:27,780 --> 00:13:29,020
it would come to this.

189
00:13:30,820 --> 00:13:32,540
I just wanted to make some money.

190
00:13:34,780 --> 00:13:35,820
I just wanted to

191
00:13:35,820 --> 00:13:36,980
pay for Songge's treatment.

192
00:13:38,020 --> 00:13:38,860
I...

193
00:13:39,940 --> 00:13:41,260
I didn't mean for this to happen.

194
00:13:43,780 --> 00:13:44,980
Along the way...

195
00:13:48,700 --> 00:13:49,700
I got in too deep.

196
00:13:50,620 --> 00:13:51,460
Every time I saw you,

197
00:13:51,460 --> 00:13:52,460
I was so scared.

198
00:13:53,320 --> 00:13:55,100
I was scared
you would see right through me.

199
00:13:55,940 --> 00:13:56,780
I...

200
00:13:57,140 --> 00:13:58,460
I was scared you would disown me.

201
00:13:59,980 --> 00:14:00,820
All these years,

202
00:14:02,740 --> 00:14:03,700
my heart...

203
00:14:06,380 --> 00:14:08,780
hasn't had a single moment of peace.

204
00:14:13,620 --> 00:14:14,460
I'm sorry.

205
00:14:16,820 --> 00:14:17,780
I'm sorry, Mr. Chen.

206
00:14:30,420 --> 00:14:31,260
Hui.

207
00:14:39,820 --> 00:14:41,140
Dad. I knew this day would come.

208
00:14:43,060 --> 00:14:44,340
Every time I thought about it,

209
00:14:47,620 --> 00:14:49,060
I was scared to death.

210
00:14:50,020 --> 00:14:51,220
But now that it's here,

211
00:14:51,820 --> 00:14:53,020
I actually feel relieved.

212
00:14:53,020 --> 00:14:54,100
Do you know why?

213
00:14:56,300 --> 00:14:58,500
I don't have to think about
how to fight you anymore.

214
00:15:06,020 --> 00:15:07,940
I don't have to wake up and think about

215
00:15:07,940 --> 00:15:09,580
using the fact
that I'm Chen Hongbing's son

216
00:15:09,580 --> 00:15:11,100
to deal with everyone else.

217
00:15:17,780 --> 00:15:18,620
Dad.

218
00:15:19,700 --> 00:15:20,700
While Mom isn't back yet,

219
00:15:23,700 --> 00:15:24,660
let them in.

220
00:15:43,820 --> 00:15:44,660
What's wrong?

221
00:15:45,020 --> 00:15:46,060
What happened?

222
00:15:56,260 --> 00:15:57,100
Mrs. Chen?

223
00:15:59,940 --> 00:16:00,780
Mrs. Chen.

224
00:16:02,940 --> 00:16:03,780
Mrs. Chen.

225
00:16:03,780 --> 00:16:04,980
Ding Yue.

226
00:16:04,980 --> 00:16:05,820
Mrs. Chen!

227
00:16:11,860 --> 00:16:12,700
Mom.

228
00:16:14,100 --> 00:16:14,940
Why are you back?

229
00:16:14,940 --> 00:16:15,860
Ding Yue.

230
00:16:16,460 --> 00:16:17,300
Chen Hongbing.

231
00:16:20,340 --> 00:16:21,420
Why did you lie to me?

232
00:16:22,540 --> 00:16:23,380
Ding Yue.

233
00:16:27,300 --> 00:16:31,580
Why did you lie to me?

234
00:16:34,000 --> 00:16:34,940
These people outside...

235
00:16:37,060 --> 00:16:37,900
Did you ask them

236
00:16:37,900 --> 00:16:38,940
to be here?

237
00:16:41,720 --> 00:16:42,820
You want to make an arrest.

238
00:16:43,260 --> 00:16:44,230
Is that it?

239
00:16:44,640 --> 00:16:46,050
You all want to arrest them, right?

240
00:16:46,250 --> 00:16:47,520
Show me the evidence!

241
00:16:47,740 --> 00:16:48,740
Without evidence,

242
00:16:48,740 --> 00:16:50,180
you are not taking my son away!

243
00:16:56,180 --> 00:16:57,780
Today is the Chinese New Year!

244
00:16:59,300 --> 00:17:00,420
Do you even understand that?

245
00:17:00,420 --> 00:17:02,380
What are you doing
on Chinese New Year's Eve?

246
00:17:02,380 --> 00:17:03,340
Why?

247
00:17:03,340 --> 00:17:04,800
Why? What are you doing?

248
00:17:04,800 --> 00:17:06,140
- Today is the Chinese New Year!
- Mom.

249
00:17:06,140 --> 00:17:08,060
- Mom.
- Chen Hongbing, what are you doing?!

250
00:17:08,060 --> 00:17:08,980
Mom, stop hitting him.

251
00:17:09,500 --> 00:17:10,180
Mom.

252
00:17:11,420 --> 00:17:12,260
Songge.

253
00:17:12,260 --> 00:17:13,630
Don't be afraid.

254
00:17:13,740 --> 00:17:14,580
Mom is here.

255
00:17:14,580 --> 00:17:16,220
I won't let them take you away.

256
00:17:16,220 --> 00:17:17,060
Mom.

257
00:17:17,220 --> 00:17:18,060
Don't be afraid.

258
00:17:20,260 --> 00:17:21,100
It's not Dad's fault.

259
00:17:22,940 --> 00:17:23,900
I committed a crime.

260
00:17:36,820 --> 00:17:37,660
You...

261
00:17:37,900 --> 00:17:38,740
You...

262
00:17:38,910 --> 00:17:40,330
What? What do you mean?

263
00:17:40,330 --> 00:17:41,240
Hui...

264
00:17:42,220 --> 00:17:43,060
That's impossible.

265
00:17:44,340 --> 00:17:46,220
My son could never commit a crime!

266
00:17:46,220 --> 00:17:48,020
You wouldn't do that.

267
00:17:48,020 --> 00:17:49,100
Say something, both of you!

268
00:17:50,380 --> 00:17:51,340
Say something!

269
00:17:51,340 --> 00:17:53,060
What do you mean?

270
00:17:53,060 --> 00:17:54,340
Hui, tell Mom.

271
00:17:54,340 --> 00:17:55,700
What do you mean?

272
00:17:55,700 --> 00:17:56,540
Hui!

273
00:17:59,340 --> 00:18:00,180
Mom.

274
00:18:01,980 --> 00:18:02,820
I'm sorry.

275
00:18:04,910 --> 00:18:05,900
I've been a terrible son.

276
00:18:08,100 --> 00:18:08,940
I'm sorry.

277
00:18:13,820 --> 00:18:14,660
Mom.

278
00:18:20,380 --> 00:18:21,220
Dad.

279
00:18:27,420 --> 00:18:28,340
I'm sorry.

280
00:18:29,140 --> 00:18:30,380
I won't be able

281
00:18:30,380 --> 00:18:31,460
to repay your kindness.

282
00:18:31,460 --> 00:18:32,460
I'm sorry.

283
00:18:35,260 --> 00:18:36,100
Ding Yue.

284
00:18:36,580 --> 00:18:37,420
Ding Yue.

285
00:18:37,420 --> 00:18:38,260
Take them away.

286
00:18:39,620 --> 00:18:40,460
Hui!

287
00:18:40,460 --> 00:18:41,620
Ding Yue!

288
00:18:41,620 --> 00:18:43,900
Hui!

289
00:18:43,900 --> 00:18:44,760
Ding Yue!

290
00:18:44,760 --> 00:18:45,900
- Mom!
- Hui!

291
00:18:45,900 --> 00:18:46,970
Hui!

292
00:19:01,220 --> 00:19:03,300
Get off me!

293
00:19:04,380 --> 00:19:05,220
Ding Yue!

294
00:19:06,220 --> 00:19:07,420
- Hui!
- Ding Yue!

295
00:19:08,020 --> 00:19:13,100
Hui!

296
00:19:20,180 --> 00:19:28,580
Hui!

297
00:19:32,380 --> 00:19:34,380
Hui!

298
00:19:38,100 --> 00:19:40,980
Hui!

299
00:19:47,140 --> 00:19:47,980
Keep moving.

300
00:19:48,660 --> 00:19:50,440
Hui!

301
00:19:50,440 --> 00:19:52,260
Chen Hongbing, let me go!

302
00:19:52,980 --> 00:19:54,780
Let me go!

303
00:19:57,140 --> 00:20:02,380
Hui!

304
00:20:10,260 --> 00:20:14,700
Hui!

305
00:20:43,940 --> 00:20:47,740
Hui!

306
00:21:24,380 --> 00:21:25,220
Zhang Wenjun, right?

307
00:21:25,820 --> 00:21:27,020
The stun baton you sold

308
00:21:27,020 --> 00:21:28,060
is tied to a murder case.

309
00:21:28,220 --> 00:21:29,820
You are hereby summoned to the bureau

310
00:21:29,820 --> 00:21:30,820
for questioning.

311
00:21:30,820 --> 00:21:32,010
Take him back for a statement.

312
00:21:32,500 --> 00:21:33,340
Let's go.

313
00:21:34,460 --> 00:21:35,300
Chief Guo.

314
00:21:36,260 --> 00:21:37,100
How did it go?

315
00:21:37,740 --> 00:21:39,100
The station just called.

316
00:21:39,100 --> 00:21:40,980
Chen Hui and Gao Songge confessed.

317
00:21:40,980 --> 00:21:42,140
That dirty money we found

318
00:21:42,140 --> 00:21:43,340
in Tian Jinhai's room

319
00:21:43,340 --> 00:21:44,500
was lent to Chen Hui.

320
00:21:45,820 --> 00:21:46,660
Good.

321
00:21:47,180 --> 00:21:48,020
Prep the paperwork.

322
00:21:48,020 --> 00:21:49,110
We're ready for prosecution.

323
00:21:49,660 --> 00:21:56,700
(Reflect on yesterday, cherish today,
and run toward tomorrow.)

324
00:22:00,660 --> 00:22:01,860
Still tastes the same.

325
00:22:06,180 --> 00:22:07,300
Slow down.

326
00:22:11,620 --> 00:22:13,020
Is it a bit too hot?

327
00:22:28,460 --> 00:22:29,940
Are you sleeping alright here?

328
00:22:31,020 --> 00:22:31,860
I'm fine.

329
00:22:32,470 --> 00:22:33,500
I couldn't sleep before.

330
00:22:34,220 --> 00:22:35,540
Now, I actually sleep soundly.

331
00:22:44,900 --> 00:22:45,740
Does it hurt?

332
00:22:49,580 --> 00:22:50,420
No.

333
00:22:52,180 --> 00:22:53,020
Liar.

334
00:22:53,660 --> 00:22:55,340
You're still lying to me.

335
00:22:58,900 --> 00:23:00,460
You've always been terrified of pain.

336
00:23:02,460 --> 00:23:03,500
When you were little

337
00:23:04,660 --> 00:23:05,660
and caught a cold,

338
00:23:06,500 --> 00:23:07,900
we'd take you to the hospital.

339
00:23:10,300 --> 00:23:11,500
Before the doctor's needle

340
00:23:13,020 --> 00:23:14,220
even touched you,

341
00:23:15,780 --> 00:23:16,900
you'd scream your head off.

342
00:23:18,780 --> 00:23:20,420
You think I don't know you?

343
00:23:33,700 --> 00:23:34,540
Dad.

344
00:23:36,300 --> 00:23:37,460
Mom. Please don't be sad.

345
00:23:38,860 --> 00:23:40,180
This was all my own choice.

346
00:23:44,580 --> 00:23:45,420
Mom.

347
00:23:45,420 --> 00:23:46,300
Stop crying.

348
00:23:47,700 --> 00:23:48,700
Your heart isn't good.

349
00:23:49,620 --> 00:23:50,620
Don't overexert yourself.

350
00:23:52,820 --> 00:23:54,340
And your back.

351
00:23:54,340 --> 00:23:55,180
You have to be careful.

352
00:23:55,180 --> 00:23:56,020
Keep it warm.

353
00:23:58,380 --> 00:23:59,220
Dad.

354
00:23:59,950 --> 00:24:01,240
While you're taking care of Mom,

355
00:24:01,460 --> 00:24:03,260
don't forget to take your insulin shots.

356
00:24:05,700 --> 00:24:06,620
Don't skimp on

357
00:24:06,620 --> 00:24:08,020
your own medication.

358
00:24:11,100 --> 00:24:11,940
I know.

359
00:24:14,660 --> 00:24:15,780
How is Songge?

360
00:24:19,500 --> 00:24:20,340
What is it?

361
00:24:21,300 --> 00:24:22,140
Nothing.

362
00:24:22,540 --> 00:24:23,540
Songge is doing great.

363
00:24:25,100 --> 00:24:26,180
Check in on her for me.

364
00:24:27,060 --> 00:24:28,100
Alright, time is up.

365
00:24:30,620 --> 00:24:31,460
Dad.

366
00:24:32,780 --> 00:24:33,620
Dad. Mom.

367
00:24:34,660 --> 00:24:35,700
Hui.

368
00:24:35,700 --> 00:24:36,900
Take good care of yourselves.

369
00:24:39,100 --> 00:24:41,660
Don't fight so much.

370
00:24:42,260 --> 00:24:43,100
Son.

371
00:24:44,620 --> 00:24:47,100
You will always be our son.

372
00:24:47,100 --> 00:24:48,100
Hui.

373
00:24:51,180 --> 00:24:52,020
Don't cry.

374
00:24:54,140 --> 00:24:54,980
Don't.

375
00:24:58,060 --> 00:24:58,900
Don't cry.

376
00:25:13,820 --> 00:25:14,980
Hui.

377
00:25:42,100 --> 00:25:43,660
I will always love you.

378
00:25:45,380 --> 00:25:46,460
We love you too.

379
00:25:59,340 --> 00:26:05,010
(Cell Area)

380
00:26:05,010 --> 00:26:07,460
(Chen Hui, Male, 23 years old.)

381
00:26:07,460 --> 00:26:10,060
(Convicted of Homicide, Smuggling,)

382
00:26:10,060 --> 00:26:17,860
(and Illegal Provision of Narcotic
and Psychotropic Drugs.)

383
00:26:17,860 --> 00:26:21,900
(Combined Punishment:
Sentenced to Death.)

384
00:26:27,020 --> 00:26:29,420
(Gao Songge, Female, 21 years old.)

385
00:26:29,420 --> 00:26:32,420
(Convicted of
Homicide (Accessory), Smuggling,)

386
00:26:32,420 --> 00:26:36,020
(and Illegal Provision of Narcotic
and Psychotropic Drugs.)

387
00:26:36,020 --> 00:26:39,060
(Combined Punishment:
Sentenced to Life Imprisonment)

388
00:26:43,820 --> 00:26:46,260
(Restricted Prison Area)

389
00:28:47,100 --> 00:28:52,780
(Five Years Later)

390
00:29:00,540 --> 00:29:01,700
Slow down!

391
00:29:01,700 --> 00:29:02,900
Don't fall!

392
00:29:02,900 --> 00:29:04,860
It's not time for that yet.

393
00:29:06,340 --> 00:29:07,180
Ding Yue.

394
00:29:08,780 --> 00:29:09,620
Yun?

395
00:29:09,620 --> 00:29:10,460
Hongbing.

396
00:29:12,180 --> 00:29:13,100
Why are you here?

397
00:29:14,740 --> 00:29:15,860
Lately, Baichun has been

398
00:29:15,860 --> 00:29:16,780
lucid one moment,

399
00:29:16,780 --> 00:29:18,340
and confused the next.

400
00:29:18,340 --> 00:29:20,020
He said he has something to tell you.

401
00:29:25,700 --> 00:29:26,540
Baichun.

402
00:29:27,140 --> 00:29:27,980
Baichun?

403
00:29:29,020 --> 00:29:30,380
Hongbing and Ding Yue are here.

404
00:29:30,860 --> 00:29:32,780
Didn't you have something to tell them?

405
00:29:33,420 --> 00:29:34,260
Wake up.

406
00:29:35,380 --> 00:29:36,300
He's right here.

407
00:29:36,300 --> 00:29:37,140
Right here.

408
00:29:37,540 --> 00:29:38,380
Baichun.

409
00:29:38,880 --> 00:29:39,900
Do you still recognize me?

410
00:29:42,180 --> 00:29:43,020
Hongbing!

411
00:29:43,300 --> 00:29:44,380
Go to the coal gangue plant.

412
00:29:44,980 --> 00:29:45,820
Hurry!

413
00:29:45,820 --> 00:29:46,660
Save Gao Ying!

414
00:29:48,220 --> 00:29:49,260
What happened to Gao Ying?

415
00:29:49,820 --> 00:29:50,660
Gao Ying!

416
00:29:51,740 --> 00:29:52,580
Fire!

417
00:29:53,660 --> 00:29:54,500
Fire!

418
00:29:54,500 --> 00:29:55,420
Go, hurry!

419
00:29:55,420 --> 00:29:56,260
Baichun.

420
00:29:57,100 --> 00:29:58,820
Were you
at the coal gangue plant that day?

421
00:30:00,780 --> 00:30:01,940
(Year 1972)
I heard you're getting married.

422
00:30:02,580 --> 00:30:03,420
Yeah.

423
00:30:03,420 --> 00:30:04,270
Tomorrow.

424
00:30:04,270 --> 00:30:05,210
Have some wedding candy.

425
00:30:05,520 --> 00:30:06,900
We're getting registered tomorrow.

426
00:30:07,220 --> 00:30:08,220
Congratulations.

427
00:30:10,100 --> 00:30:11,020
Well,

428
00:30:11,020 --> 00:30:13,340
since you're here,
I actually wanted to ask you something.

429
00:30:14,040 --> 00:30:16,420
When you guys make that
old-fashioned bread in the kitchen,

430
00:30:16,420 --> 00:30:17,860
you use glycerin, right?

431
00:30:17,860 --> 00:30:18,740
Yeah.

432
00:30:18,740 --> 00:30:22,060
(Fengyang Coal Mine Guesthouse)

433
00:30:22,060 --> 00:30:23,700
Could you get me some?

434
00:30:24,500 --> 00:30:25,620
What do you need it for?

435
00:30:26,900 --> 00:30:28,500
My dad has had this skin condition

436
00:30:28,500 --> 00:30:29,340
for years.

437
00:30:29,780 --> 00:30:30,660
If he doesn't rub

438
00:30:30,660 --> 00:30:31,860
something moisturizing on it,

439
00:30:31,860 --> 00:30:33,260
it hurts and itches terribly.

440
00:30:33,260 --> 00:30:34,780
And clam oil is too expensive,

441
00:30:34,780 --> 00:30:35,860
we can't afford it.

442
00:30:36,100 --> 00:30:36,940
Sure.

443
00:30:36,940 --> 00:30:37,820
No problem.

444
00:30:37,820 --> 00:30:38,660
Tell you what.

445
00:30:38,660 --> 00:30:39,520
Tomorrow,

446
00:30:39,520 --> 00:30:40,970
wait for me at the coal gangue plant.

447
00:30:40,970 --> 00:30:41,820
Bring a bottle,

448
00:30:41,820 --> 00:30:42,940
and I'll pour you some.

449
00:30:42,940 --> 00:30:43,780
Really?

450
00:30:44,700 --> 00:30:46,100
Just don't tell anyone.

451
00:30:46,100 --> 00:30:47,140
Don't worry.

452
00:30:47,140 --> 00:30:48,140
Hold on.

453
00:30:48,140 --> 00:30:50,260
Here, take it all.

454
00:30:55,420 --> 00:30:56,260
See you tomorrow!

455
00:31:00,620 --> 00:31:01,780
Thanks.

456
00:31:02,340 --> 00:31:04,260
Don't be so polite?

457
00:31:04,260 --> 00:31:05,100
Here.

458
00:31:09,020 --> 00:31:09,900
I'm so sorry!

459
00:31:09,900 --> 00:31:10,740
It's fine.

460
00:31:10,740 --> 00:31:12,010
- No big deal.
- Let me wipe it for you.

461
00:31:12,010 --> 00:31:12,860
It's really fine.

462
00:31:13,660 --> 00:31:14,980
What are you doing?

463
00:31:15,380 --> 00:31:16,780
Well, my clothes were already dirty.

464
00:31:17,420 --> 00:31:18,780
I have to go for my registration.

465
00:31:18,780 --> 00:31:19,660
I should go.

466
00:31:19,660 --> 00:31:21,100
- What are you doing?
- Listen to me!

467
00:31:21,260 --> 00:31:22,100
What are you doing?

468
00:31:22,340 --> 00:31:23,180
Wait.

469
00:31:23,180 --> 00:31:24,900
- What are you doing?
- Don't marry him, okay?

470
00:31:24,910 --> 00:31:26,180
I like you too.

471
00:31:26,350 --> 00:31:27,250
Let go!

472
00:31:27,250 --> 00:31:28,100
What are you doing?

473
00:31:28,900 --> 00:31:30,540
Just don't marry him, okay?

474
00:31:30,540 --> 00:31:31,700
Stop it!

475
00:31:33,050 --> 00:31:33,950
What are you doing?

476
00:31:33,950 --> 00:31:34,810
Let go!

477
00:31:36,620 --> 00:31:37,460
You little punk!

478
00:31:37,460 --> 00:31:38,330
Assaulting a woman

479
00:31:38,330 --> 00:31:39,220
in broad daylight?

480
00:31:39,220 --> 00:31:40,220
I'm not assaulting her.

481
00:31:40,900 --> 00:31:41,740
We work together.

482
00:31:41,740 --> 00:31:42,780
We're just messing around.

483
00:31:42,860 --> 00:31:44,100
You call this messing around?

484
00:31:44,700 --> 00:31:46,060
You're obviously harassing her!

485
00:31:46,060 --> 00:31:47,570
Miss, tell me what he did to you.

486
00:31:47,570 --> 00:31:48,420
Gao Ying!

487
00:31:48,420 --> 00:31:49,580
Say something!

488
00:31:50,900 --> 00:31:52,060
It's fine, just let him go.

489
00:31:52,620 --> 00:31:53,460
Don't be afraid.

490
00:31:53,460 --> 00:31:54,300
Miss.

491
00:31:54,420 --> 00:31:55,980
I'm the mine's safety officer.

492
00:31:55,980 --> 00:31:57,940
Let's go to the security office together
and clear this up.

493
00:31:57,940 --> 00:31:59,040
- Let's go.
- Gao Ying.

494
00:31:59,140 --> 00:32:00,320
No, don't.

495
00:32:00,400 --> 00:32:02,140
I'm getting
my marriage registration soon.

496
00:32:02,500 --> 00:32:04,140
My fiancé is also
in the security office.

497
00:32:04,140 --> 00:32:05,140
He has a bad temper.

498
00:32:05,140 --> 00:32:06,940
I don't want him to cause a scene.

499
00:32:06,940 --> 00:32:08,140
Forget it, just let him go.

500
00:32:09,900 --> 00:32:10,740
Get lost!

501
00:32:13,500 --> 00:32:14,540
Shameless jerk.

502
00:32:19,420 --> 00:32:20,580
Is this yours?

503
00:32:21,940 --> 00:32:22,900
It's mine.

504
00:32:22,900 --> 00:32:24,040
- Keep it safe.
- Thank you.

505
00:32:24,040 --> 00:32:25,170
Come to me if anything happens.

506
00:32:25,180 --> 00:32:26,020
Okay?

507
00:32:26,020 --> 00:32:26,860
(Fengyang Coal Mine)
Thank you.

508
00:32:49,740 --> 00:32:50,860
What did you do?!

509
00:32:50,860 --> 00:32:51,940
I didn't do anything!

510
00:32:51,940 --> 00:32:53,340
She just caught on fire by herself!

511
00:32:57,100 --> 00:32:57,940
She's on fire!

512
00:32:58,380 --> 00:32:59,220
Let's go!

513
00:32:59,220 --> 00:33:00,460
It's too late!

514
00:33:00,460 --> 00:33:01,500
We have to save her!

515
00:33:01,500 --> 00:33:02,340
Let's go!

516
00:33:02,620 --> 00:33:03,460
No!

517
00:33:08,260 --> 00:33:09,100
Where are you going?!

518
00:33:09,980 --> 00:33:10,820
Stop right there!

519
00:33:27,260 --> 00:33:29,220
Turn back!

520
00:33:29,220 --> 00:33:30,180
I have to go report this!

521
00:33:30,180 --> 00:33:31,740
Are you crazy?

522
00:33:31,740 --> 00:33:33,660
Who's going to believe you?

523
00:33:33,660 --> 00:33:35,060
She's a human being!

524
00:33:35,060 --> 00:33:36,100
You assaulted her!

525
00:33:36,100 --> 00:33:36,980
It wasn't me!

526
00:33:36,980 --> 00:33:38,380
I didn't assault her!

527
00:33:38,380 --> 00:33:40,060
I could say you assaulted her!

528
00:33:40,580 --> 00:33:42,460
My dad is the mine director!

529
00:33:42,460 --> 00:33:43,900
Let's see who they believe!

530
00:33:48,140 --> 00:33:48,980
Then what do we do?

531
00:33:48,980 --> 00:33:51,700
As long as neither of us talks,
no one will ever know.

532
00:33:55,520 --> 00:33:57,020
Go to the coal gangue plant right now!

533
00:33:57,380 --> 00:33:58,460
You can still save her!

534
00:33:59,060 --> 00:34:00,100
Go, hurry!

535
00:34:00,820 --> 00:34:02,220
Don't wait, it'll be too late!

536
00:34:02,780 --> 00:34:03,620
Go save her!

537
00:34:03,620 --> 00:34:04,460
Hurry!

538
00:34:04,660 --> 00:34:05,540
Hongbing.

539
00:34:05,540 --> 00:34:06,610
I'm so sorry.

540
00:34:06,910 --> 00:34:07,810
You have to believe me.

541
00:34:07,810 --> 00:34:09,100
Everything I'm saying is true.

542
00:34:13,380 --> 00:34:14,240
Yun.

543
00:34:14,240 --> 00:34:15,090
Hongbing.

544
00:34:15,090 --> 00:34:15,950
We're leaving.

545
00:34:18,140 --> 00:34:18,980
Hongbing!

546
00:34:18,980 --> 00:34:19,840
Don't go!

547
00:34:19,840 --> 00:34:21,500
Hongbing! Hongbing!

548
00:34:21,500 --> 00:34:22,340
Don't go!

549
00:34:22,410 --> 00:34:23,340
Hurry and save her!

550
00:34:23,460 --> 00:34:24,700
Hurry, there's still time!

551
00:34:24,700 --> 00:34:25,740
Hurry!

552
00:34:25,740 --> 00:34:26,900
Go save her!

553
00:34:26,900 --> 00:34:28,620
Hurry up and save her!

554
00:34:28,620 --> 00:34:30,100
Go save her!

555
00:34:30,100 --> 00:34:31,460
Or else it'll be too late!

556
00:34:31,590 --> 00:34:32,510
- Chun!
- Hongbing!

557
00:34:32,660 --> 00:34:33,950
If you leave, she's done for!

558
00:34:34,580 --> 00:34:36,420
Save her! Save her!

559
00:34:36,420 --> 00:34:37,300
- Baichun!
- Save her!

560
00:34:37,300 --> 00:34:38,160
Baichun!

561
00:34:38,160 --> 00:34:39,100
Hurry, save her!

562
00:34:39,700 --> 00:34:40,740
It's me!

563
00:34:40,740 --> 00:34:42,180
It's me, Yun.

564
00:34:44,180 --> 00:34:46,300
Calm down. Calm down.

565
00:34:46,300 --> 00:34:47,140
I'm sorry.

566
00:35:04,100 --> 00:35:05,580
(Year 1972)
Dr. Shao,

567
00:35:05,580 --> 00:35:06,900
I have two physical exam forms here.

568
00:35:06,900 --> 00:35:08,300
Could you stamp them for me, please?

569
00:35:08,300 --> 00:35:09,340
Comrade Ding Yue,

570
00:35:09,340 --> 00:35:10,180
I'm going to lunch.

571
00:35:10,180 --> 00:35:11,110
Come back this afternoon.

572
00:35:11,150 --> 00:35:12,130
Please.

573
00:35:12,340 --> 00:35:13,740
These are two good friends of mine.

574
00:35:13,740 --> 00:35:15,530
They're in a rush to get their license.

575
00:35:15,660 --> 00:35:16,500
Thank you.

576
00:35:16,500 --> 00:35:17,340
(Chen Hongbing, Physical Exam Form)
Alright.

577
00:35:17,340 --> 00:35:18,620
I'm doing this as a favor to you.

578
00:35:19,140 --> 00:35:20,220
When they get married,

579
00:35:20,580 --> 00:35:21,620
pass out the wedding candy.

580
00:35:21,620 --> 00:35:22,460
Of course!

581
00:35:22,460 --> 00:35:24,060
(Fengyang Coal Mine Workers' Hospital)
We'd never forget yours.

582
00:35:24,870 --> 00:35:25,860
Here, all stamped.

583
00:35:27,420 --> 00:35:28,540
Thank you.

584
00:35:28,540 --> 00:35:29,540
Don't mention it.

585
00:35:29,540 --> 00:35:30,380
Ding Yue,

586
00:35:30,460 --> 00:35:31,460
you have to come

587
00:35:31,460 --> 00:35:32,580
to our wedding.

588
00:35:32,580 --> 00:35:33,660
Absolutely.

589
00:35:35,500 --> 00:35:36,340
Gao Ying.

590
00:35:36,720 --> 00:35:38,020
Can I talk to you for a second?

591
00:35:40,340 --> 00:35:42,100
What's the big secret?

592
00:35:42,100 --> 00:35:43,540
You're getting married,

593
00:35:43,540 --> 00:35:45,220
so I'm giving you a practical gift.

594
00:35:48,380 --> 00:35:49,660
Potassium permanganate.

595
00:35:49,660 --> 00:35:50,500
This...

596
00:35:51,020 --> 00:35:51,980
What is this?

597
00:35:52,580 --> 00:35:53,450
After you get married,

598
00:35:53,450 --> 00:35:55,160
feminine hygiene is
incredibly important.

599
00:35:55,300 --> 00:35:57,140
Otherwise, you won't be able
to have kids,

600
00:35:57,140 --> 00:35:59,020
and you'll be on medication forever.

601
00:35:59,020 --> 00:36:00,460
What are you talking about?

602
00:36:00,720 --> 00:36:02,020
- It's true!
- Stop jinxing me!

603
00:36:03,580 --> 00:36:04,420
I'm leaving.

604
00:36:07,020 --> 00:36:07,860
Ding Yue.

605
00:36:07,860 --> 00:36:09,100
Thank you.

606
00:36:09,100 --> 00:36:10,140
Wishing you both happiness.

607
00:36:13,120 --> 00:36:14,260
What were you talking about?

608
00:36:14,260 --> 00:36:15,260
Nothing.

609
00:36:26,540 --> 00:36:28,220
Today, I finally understand

610
00:36:29,140 --> 00:36:30,920
what really happened
to Gao Ying back then.

611
00:36:33,460 --> 00:36:35,020
Can't you show some reaction?

612
00:36:40,580 --> 00:36:42,420
Time is a powerful thing.

613
00:36:45,140 --> 00:36:46,900
As long as your conscience is clear,

614
00:36:49,580 --> 00:36:51,940
no matter how fixated you are
on a person or an event,

615
00:36:55,020 --> 00:36:56,540
you'll be able to let it go.

616
00:37:00,700 --> 00:37:02,820
Don't you hate Yang Baichun at all?

617
00:37:05,460 --> 00:37:06,540
Why would I hate him?

618
00:37:09,300 --> 00:37:10,220
For him,

619
00:37:11,300 --> 00:37:12,620
time

620
00:37:12,620 --> 00:37:13,900
is purgatory.

621
00:37:15,740 --> 00:37:16,900
His whole life...

622
00:37:20,460 --> 00:37:22,260
will forever be stuck on that day.

623
00:37:24,180 --> 00:37:25,100
And his conscience...

624
00:37:26,780 --> 00:37:28,020
will continue

625
00:37:28,020 --> 00:37:29,700
to burn in that fire.

626
00:37:41,860 --> 00:37:43,260
If I hadn't

627
00:37:43,260 --> 00:37:45,660
given that to Gao Ying back then,

628
00:37:45,660 --> 00:37:46,500
perhaps none of this

629
00:37:46,500 --> 00:37:48,140
would've happened.

630
00:37:49,740 --> 00:37:51,620
Life doesn't have "what ifs."

631
00:37:51,620 --> 00:37:52,980
(The End)

632
00:37:52,980 --> 00:37:54,580
We can only move forward.

633
00:37:54,580 --> 00:37:59,900
(The End)

634
00:38:14,750 --> 00:38:17,600
♪You ask what is outside the window♪

635
00:38:18,590 --> 00:38:21,490
♪You ask what color the light is♪

636
00:38:21,490 --> 00:38:26,230
♪You say hope is a dancing bubble♪

637
00:38:28,740 --> 00:38:31,070
♪So colorful and free♪

638
00:38:32,030 --> 00:38:36,860
♪Yet popping at a single touch♪

639
00:38:38,340 --> 00:38:43,510
♪So I hope this world protects me♪

640
00:38:45,150 --> 00:38:49,910
♪Just like
when we were innocent children♪

641
00:38:52,320 --> 00:38:55,250
♪Back then, the distance was in sight♪

642
00:38:55,690 --> 00:38:58,590
♪The road had no end♪

643
00:38:58,590 --> 00:39:01,380
♪Say "see you tomorrow"♪

644
00:39:01,680 --> 00:39:06,420
♪And there would surely be a future♪

645
00:39:07,560 --> 00:39:10,660
♪The moonlight shines on the bed♪

646
00:39:10,840 --> 00:39:14,100
♪Memories tucked in an old pocket♪

647
00:39:14,290 --> 00:39:17,320
♪Wind whistling through empty sleeves♪

648
00:39:17,660 --> 00:39:21,750
♪Just pretend
you're holding my hand again♪

649
00:39:21,910 --> 00:39:25,000
♪The moonlight shines on the bed♪

650
00:39:25,290 --> 00:39:28,270
♪Flames flicker, the heart feels hollow♪

651
00:39:28,670 --> 00:39:32,070
♪Climbing high towers,
wandering alleyways♪

652
00:39:32,340 --> 00:39:46,620
♪The four seasons remain,
but people have grown old♪
